### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Get Professions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/run/professions

###

### Get Relic Templates
GET http://localhost:3000/api/run/relics

###

### Get Profession Relics (e.g., WARRIOR)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/run/professions/WARRIOR/relics

###

### Initialize Run
POST http://localhost:3000/api/run/init
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "professionId": "WARRIOR",
  "seed": 12345,
  "startingRelicIds": ["relic_warrior_resolute_heart"]
}

###

### Buy Item
POST http://localhost:3000/api/run/shop/buy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runId": "run_abc123",
  "itemId": "item_example"
}

###

### Sell Item
POST http://localhost:3000/api/run/shop/sell
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runId": "run_abc123",
  "itemId": "item_example"
}

###

### Refresh Shop
POST http://localhost:3000/api/run/shop/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runId": "run_abc123"
}

